OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWomen's safety: 'I begged  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthe bus driver to let me   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftravel home safely'        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A disabled woman is calling for greater
OL,6, understanding of female safety after   
OL,7, she "begged" a bus driver to let her   
OL,8, travel home when her pass did not work.
OL,10,FRachel Davies's pass was declined when 
OL,11,Fshe tried to take the first of two     
OL,12,Fbuses home, in Northampton. The        
OL,13,FStagecoach driver let her travel to her
OL,14,Ffirst stop but could not help further. 
OL,16,FShe said a "transition plan" was needed
OL,17,Fto ensure journeys were completed.     
OL,19,FStagecoach said the driver had been    
OL,20,F"following the rules".                 
